Class LinkedList<T>

java.lang.Object
LinkedList<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Collection<T>, Iterable<T>, List<T>
public class LinkedList<T> extends Object implements List<T>
This is HW4. 5/10/2022 This class implements List. This Linked List will create a series of nodes and link them together. As well perform a various other functions such as adding, removing, and smaller functions.
